data.description: Escape to the country as this home offers tranquility and comfort amidst natural beauty. Motivated Seller offering $4K in Closing Costs to potential buyers!! Charming 1-story Ranch home with finished 2-car  garage,, in McGees Elementary, McGees Middle, & W. Johnston School district.  Spacious living area that incorporates a wonderful open floor plan.   Large Livingroom area, kitchen with central island & walk in pantry, granite countertops, tile backsplash & undercounter lighting: the owner's suite has custom wood shelving in the walk in closet, w/a huge tile-shower & dual vanity in the bathroom. Tile floors in baths & laundry room. 2 additional bedrooms w/ walk in closets; Also additional flex / office room that can be used for multiple purposes-You decide!! The dining area opens to a covered rear porch- perfect for relaxing, a double patio- for all your grilling needs, and a HUGE 6 ft privacy fence!!  Home located near the I-40/ Exit 319 /Hwy 210 w/easy access to Raleigh & RTP. Seller Offering closing costs to buyers! Are you needing a HUGE backyard? Fenced in!! Privacy!!! For Safety & Fun!! Here's the ONE!! Your gonna say '' Wow, this is an incredible backyard with lots of potential!!  Contact our real estate agent today to schedule a viewing and make this rural retreat your own!
